<p>345. At the resumed organizational meeting of the seventh session, held on 28 February 2008, 
the selection of the troika members for the universal periodic review was conducted in 
accordance with paragraph 18 (d) of Council resolution 5/1 (for the results of the selection of 
troikas, see the annex to the final report). </p>

